com.team23.weather.mars

Interface IMarsWeatherClient

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MarsWeatherClient

    public interface IMarsWeatherClient
    An IMarsWeatherClient is an object that contains the url of NASA's archive of Mars Weather information. This client can read the weather and return it back to another function in a readable format.
    Author:
    Andrew Bloch-Hansen, Saquib Mian
    See Also:
    MarsWeatherClient, MarsWeatherResponse, Report, MarsForecast, ISerializer, HttpClient
